{"tid":1419561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急！求片！幫推！］前晚將軍澳速龍爆街坊頭","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T01:55:19.000Z","uid":10843,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd44283ff54c6c142e01cfdaa0202c2613034b1","tid":1419561,"uid":10843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5OcVBEk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OcVBEk.png&h=d1a75626&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dwfj3jk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdwfj3jk.png&h=c8c94f90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係八月四日，晚上11:00左右喺將軍澳寶順路，俾速龍爆頭嘅街坊親屬<br />\n<br />\n我地而家好需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 收集大家當時現場的相關照片同影片(其他平台見到cap俾我都得)<br />\n<br />\n2⃣. 如果你喺現場，方便請留低一個聯絡方式<br />\n(可以pm我telegram account，可以fact check我地身份，資料絕對保密)<br />\n以便日後還原事件<br />\n<br />\n請大家合力幫忙發資訊喺<br />\n呢個telegram gp: <a href=\"http://t.me/injury0804gp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finjury0804gp&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=9c19c7ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/injury0804gp</a><br />\n或pm呢個tg account : @tkoinjury<br />\n或email: 0804injury@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n我地會保留一切 追究警方 嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fe403687d25351e0aac1dc461b24cd635273f4","tid":1419561,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:53:20.000Z","msg":"將軍澳係普通防暴黎"},{"pid":"b508c551343ee5a32a328b07fef7113b1e236137","tid":1419561,"uid":267501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"熟人，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i